Package: kadu
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kadu-common (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends: kadu-external-modules (>= 0.6.0~rc3-1), kadu-kde-modules
Conflicts: kadu-external-modules (<= 0.6.0~rc3-1)
Suggests: kadu-themes
Description: Gadu-Gadu client for X11
 Gadu-Gadu is a Windows instant messenger, very popular in Poland.
 Kadu is a QT3 version for *nix systems.
 .
 This package provides Kadu along with modules developed by Kadu developers.

